msgstr "ປັບຂະໜາດລະບົບໄຟລ໌ເທິງ %(device)s ສຳເລັດແລ້ວ"

#: ../blivet/deviceaction.py:947
msgid "add container member"
msgstr "ເພີ່ມສະມາຊິກຄອນເທນເນີ"

#: ../blivet/deviceaction.py:1012
msgid "remove container member"
msgstr "ເອົາສະມາຊິກຄອນເທນເນີອອກ"

#: ../blivet/deviceaction.py:1082
msgid "configure format"
msgstr "ກຳນົດຄ່າຮູບແບບ"

#: ../blivet/deviceaction.py:1153
msgid "configure device"
msgstr "ກຳນົດຄ່າອຸປະກອນ"

#: ../blivet/errors.py:223
msgid ""
"This is usually caused by cloning the device image resulting in duplication "
"of the UUID value which should be unique. In that case you can either "
"disconnect one of the devices or reformat it."
msgstr ""
"ສິ່ງນີ້ມັກຈະເກີດຈາກການສຳເນົາ (cloning) ອິເມຈຂອງອຸປະກອນ ເຮັດໃຫ້ມີຄ່າ UUID ຊໍ້າກັນ ເຊິ່ງຕາມຈິງແລ້ວມັ"
"ນຄວນຈະມີພຽງໜຶ່ງດຽວ. ໃນກໍລະນີນີ້ ເຈົ້າສາມາດເລືອກຕັດການເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ອຸປະກອນອັນໃດອັນໜຶ່ງ ຫຼື ຟໍແມັດມັນໃໝ່ກໍໄດ້."

#: ../blivet/errors.py:230
msgid ""
"For some reason we were unable to locate a disklabel on a disk that the "
"kernel is reporting partitions on. It is unclear what the exact problem is. "
"Please file a bug at http://bugzilla.redhat.com"
msgstr ""
"ດ້ວຍເຫດຜົນບາງຢ່າງ ພວກເຮົາບໍ່ສາມາດຊອກຫາປ້າຍຊື່ດິສ (disklabel) ເທິງດິສທີ່ເຄີເນລ (kernel) ລາຍງາ"
"ນວ່າມີພາທິຊັນຢູ່. ບໍ່ຊັດເຈນວ່າບັນຫາທີ່ແທ້ຈິງແມ່ນຫຍັງ. ກະລຸນາແຈ້ງບັກໄດ້ທີ່ http://bugzilla.redhat.com"

#: ../blivet/errors.py:237
msgid ""
"Either restore the disklabel to a completely working state or remove it "
"completely.\n"
"Hint: parted can restore it or wipefs can remove it."
msgstr ""
"ເລືອກກູ້ຄືນປ້າຍຊື່ດິສໃຫ້ກັບມາໃຊ້ງານໄດ້ສົມບູນ ຫຼື ລຶບມັນອອກໃຫ້ໝົດ.\n"
"ຄຳແນະນຳ: ສາມາດໃຊ້ parted ເພື່ອກູ້ຄືນ ຫຼື ໃຊ້ wipefs ເພື່ອລຶບອອກ."

#: ../blivet/errors.py:243
msgid ""
"Rename one of the volume groups so the names are distinct.\n"
"Hint 1: vgrename accepts UUID in place of the old name.\n"
"Hint 2: You can get the VG UUIDs by running 'pvs -o +vg_uuid'."
msgstr ""
"ປ່ຽນຊື່ຂອງກຸ່ມວໍລຸມ (volume group) ອັນໃດອັນໜຶ່ງ ເພື່ອໃຫ້ຊື່ບໍ່ຊໍ້າກັນ.\n"
"ຄຳແນະນຳ 1: vgrename ສາມາດໃຊ້ UUID ແທນຊື່ເກົ່າໄດ້.\n"
"ຄຳແນະນຳ 2: ເຈົ້າສາມາດເບິ່ງ VG UUID ໄດ້ໂດຍການລັນຄຳສັ່ງ 'pvs -o +vg_uuid'."

#: ../blivet/errors.py:251
msgid ""
"All parent devices must be selected when choosing exclusive or ignored disks "
"for a multipath or firmware RAID device."
msgstr ""
"ຕ້ອງເລືອກອຸປະກອນແມ່ (parent devices) ທັງໝົດ ເມື່ອເລືອກດິສແບບສະເພາະ (exclusive) ຫຼື ດິສທີ່ຖືກລ"
"ະເວັ້ນ ສຳລັບອຸປະກອນ multipath ຫຼື firmware RAID."

#: ../blivet/fcoe.py:122
msgid "FCoE not available"
msgstr "FCoE ບໍ່ພ້ອມໃຊ້ງານ"

#: ../blivet/iscsi.py:216
msgid "Unable to change iSCSI initiator name once set"
msgstr "ບໍ່ສາມາດປ່ຽນຊື່ iSCSI initiator ໄດ້ຫຼັງຈາກທີ່ໄດ້ກຳນົດໄປແລ້ວ"

#: ../blivet/iscsi.py:218
msgid "Must provide an iSCSI initiator name"
msgstr "ຕ້ອງລະບຸຊື່ iSCSI initiator"

#: ../blivet/iscsi.py:412
msgid "iSCSI not available"
msgstr "iSCSI ບໍ່ພ້ອມໃຊ້ງານ"

#: ../blivet/iscsi.py:414
msgid "No initiator name set"
msgstr "ບໍ່ມີການກຳນົດຊື່ initiator"

#: ../blivet/iscsi.py:532
msgid "No iSCSI nodes discovered"
msgstr "ບໍ່ພົບໂນດ iSCSI"

#: ../blivet/iscsi.py:552
msgid "No new iSCSI nodes discovered"
msgstr "ບໍ່ພົບໂນດ iSCSI ໃໝ່"

#: ../blivet/iscsi.py:555
msgid "Could not log in to any of the discovered nodes"
msgstr "ບໍ່ສາມາດເຂົ້າສູ່ລະບົບໂນດໃດໆທີ່ຄົ້ນພົບໄດ້"

#: ../blivet/partitioning.py:455
msgid "unable to allocate aligned partition"
msgstr "ບໍ່ສາມາດຈັດສັນພາທິຊັນໃຫ້ຕົງຕາມຂອບ (aligned)"

#: ../blivet/partitioning.py:463
msgid "requested size exceeds maximum allowed"
msgstr "ຂະໜາດທີ່ຮ້ອງຂໍເກີນກວ່າຄ່າສູງສຸດທີ່ອະນຸຍາດ"

#: ../blivet/partitioning.py:475
#, python-format
msgid "failed to add partition to disk: %s"
msgstr "ບໍ່ສາມາດເພີ່ມພາທິຊັນໃສ່ດິສ: %s"

#: ../blivet/partitioning.py:586
#, python-format
msgid "disk %s inaccessible"
msgstr "ດິສ %s ບໍ່ສາມາດເຂົ້າເຖິງໄດ້"

#: ../blivet/partitioning.py:647
#, python-format
msgid ""
"partition is too small for %(format)s formatting (allowable size is "
"%(min_size)s to %(max_size)s)"
msgstr ""
"ພາທິຊັນມີຂະໜາດນ້ອຍເກີນໄປສຳລັບການຟໍແມັດ %(format)s (ຂະໜາດທີ່ອະນຸຍາດແມ່ນ %(min_size)s ຫາ %"
"(max_size)s)"

#: ../blivet/partitioning.py:652
#, python-format
msgid ""
"partition is too large for %(format)s formatting (allowable size is "
"%(min_size)s to %(max_size)s)"
msgstr ""
"ພາທິຊັນມີຂະໜາດໃຫຍ່ເກີນໄປສຳລັບການຟໍແມັດ %(format)s (ຂະໜາດທີ່ອະນຸຍາດແມ່ນ %(min_size)s ຫາ %"
"(max_size)s)"

#: ../blivet/partitioning.py:971
msgid "Unable to allocate requested partition scheme."
msgstr "ບໍ່ສາມາດຈັດສັນຮູບແບບພາທິຊັນຕາມທີ່ຮ້ອງຂໍໄດ້."

#: ../blivet/partitioning.py:1006
msgid "not enough free space after creating extended partition"
msgstr "ເນື້ອທີ່ວ່າງບໍ່ພຽງພໍຫຼັງຈາກສ້າງ extended partition"

#: ../blivet/partitioning.py:1013
msgid "failed to allocate aligned partition"
msgstr "ການຈັດສັນພາທິຊັນໃຫ້ຕົງຕາມຂອບ (aligned) ລົ້ມເຫຼວ"

#: ../blivet/partitioning.py:1214
msgid "cannot reclaim more than request has grown"
msgstr "ບໍ່ສາມາດຮຽກຄືນເນື້ອທີ່ໄດ້ຫຼາຍກວ່າຈຳນວນທີ່ຮ້ອງຂໍເພີ່ມຂຶ້ນ"

#: ../blivet/partitioning.py:1428
msgid "DiskChunk requests must be of type PartitionRequest"
msgstr "ການຮ້ອງຂໍ DiskChunk ຕ້ອງເປັນປະເພດ PartitionRequest"

#: ../blivet/partitioning.py:1441
msgid "partitions allocated outside disklabel limits"
msgstr "ພາທິຊັນຖືກຈັດສັນຢູ່ນອກຂອບເຂດຂອງປ້າຍຊື່ດິສ (disklabel)"

#: ../blivet/partitioning.py:1526
msgid "VGChunk requests must be of type LVRequest"
msgstr "ການຮ້ອງຂໍ VGChunk ຕ້ອງເປັນປະເພດ LVRequest"

#. by now we have allocated the PVs so if there isn't enough
#. space in the VG we have a real problem
#: ../blivet/partitioning.py:2018
msgid "not enough space for LVM requests"
msgstr "ເນື້ອທີ່ບໍ່ພຽງພໍສຳລັບການຮ້ອງຂໍ LVM"

#: ../blivet/zfcp.py:106
msgid "You have not specified a device number or the number is invalid"
msgstr "ເຈົ້າຍັງບໍ່ໄດ້ລະບຸໝາຍເລກອຸປະກອນ ຫຼື ໝາຍເລກບໍ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ"

#: ../blivet/zfcp.py:131
#, python-format
msgid "zFCP device %s not found, not even in device ignore list."
msgstr "ບໍ່ພົບອຸປະກອນ zFCP %s ແລະ ບໍ່ມີຢູ່ໃນລາຍການອຸປະກອນທີ່ໃຫ້ລະເວັ້ນ."

#: ../blivet/zfcp.py:146
#, python-format
msgid "Could not set zFCP device %(devnum)s online (%(e)s)."
msgstr "ບໍ່ສາມາດຕັ້ງຄ່າອຸປະກອນ zFCP %(devnum)s ໃຫ້ອອນໄລນ໌ໄດ້ (%(e)s)."

#: ../blivet/zfcp.py:159
#, python-format
msgid "Could not set zFCP device %(devnum)s offline (%(e)s)."
msgstr "ບໍ່ສາມາດຕັ້ງຄ່າອຸປະກອນ zFCP %(devnum)s ໃຫ້ອອຟໄລນ໌ໄດ້ (%(e)s)."

#: ../blivet/zfcp.py:218
msgid "You have not specified a worldwide port name or the name is invalid."
msgstr "ເຈົ້າຍັງບໍ່ໄດ້ລະບຸຊື່ worldwide port ຫຼື ຊື່ບໍ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ."

#: ../blivet/zfcp.py:222
msgid "You have not specified a FCP LUN or the number is invalid."
msgstr "ເຈົ້າຍັງບໍ່ໄດ້ລະບຸ FCP LUN ຫຼື ໝາຍເລກບໍ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ."

#: ../blivet/zfcp.py:268
#, python-format
msgid "Could not add WWPN %(wwpn)s to zFCP device %(devnum)s (%(e)s)."
msgstr "ບໍ່ສາມາດເພີ່ມ WWPN %(wwpn)s ໃສ່ອຸປະກອນ zFCP %(devnum)s ໄດ້ (%(e)s)."

#. newer zfcp sysfs interface with auto port scan
#: ../blivet/zfcp.py:275
#, python-format
msgid "WWPN %(wwpn)s not found at zFCP device %(devnum)s."
msgstr "ບໍ່ພົບ WWPN %(wwpn)s ທີ່ອຸປະກອນ zFCP %(devnum)s."

#: ../blivet/zfcp.py:291
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Could not add LUN %(fcplun)s to WWPN %(wwpn)s on zFCP device %(devnum)s "
"(%(e)s)."
msgstr ""
"ບໍ່ສາມາດເພີ່ມ LUN %(fcplun)s ໃສ່ WWPN %(wwpn)s ເທິງອຸປະກອນ zFCP %(devnum)s ໄດ້ (%(e)"
"s)."

#: ../blivet/zfcp.py:297
#, python-format
msgid ""
"LUN %(fcplun)s at WWPN %(wwpn)s on zFCP device %(devnum)s already configured."
msgstr ""
"LUN %(fcplun)s ທີ່ WWPN %(wwpn)s ເທິງອຸປະກອນ zFCP %(devnum)s ຖືກກຳນົດຄ່າໄວ້ແລ້ວ."

#: ../blivet/zfcp.py:310
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Could not read failed attribute of LUN %(fcplun)s at WWPN %(wwpn)s on zFCP "
"device %(devnum)s (%(e)s)."
msgstr ""
"ບໍ່ສາມາດອ່ານຄຸນລັກສະນະທີ່ລົ້ມເຫຼວຂອງ LUN %(fcplun)s ທີ່ WWPN %(wwpn)s ເທິງອຸປະກອນ zFCP %"
"(devnum)s ໄດ້ (%(e)s)."

#: ../blivet/zfcp.py:319
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Failed LUN %(fcplun)s at WWPN %(wwpn)s on zFCP device %(devnum)s removed "
"again."
msgstr ""
"LUN %(fcplun)s ທີ່ລົ້ມເຫຼວຢູ່ WWPN %(wwpn)s ເທິງອຸປະກອນ zFCP %(devnum)s ຖືກລຶບອອກອີກຄັ້ງ."

#: ../blivet/zfcp.py:339
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Could not correctly delete SCSI device of zFCP %(devnum)s %(wwpn)s "
"%(fcplun)s (%(e)s)."
msgstr ""
"ບໍ່ສາມາດລຶບອຸປະກອນ SCSI ຂອງ zFCP %(devnum)s %(wwpn)s %(fcplun)s ໄດ້ຢ່າງຖືກຕ້ອງ (%(e)"
"s)."

#: ../blivet/zfcp.py:349
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Could not remove LUN %(fcplun)s at WWPN %(wwpn)s on zFCP device %(devnum)s "
"(%(e)s)."
msgstr ""
"ບໍ່ສາມາດລຶບ LUN %(fcplun)s ທີ່ WWPN %(wwpn)s ເທິງອຸປະກອນ zFCP %(devnum)s ໄດ້ (%(e)s)."

#: ../blivet/zfcp.py:368
